rows.name:
D'you think we can really make
a whole school by ourselves?

rows.label: qst104208_msg0101
rows.name:
I just need ore. Doesn't matter what
type, apparently. Have you got any?

rows.label: qst104208_msg0121
rows.name:
Mmm...I don't think I've got as much
as Mason wanted yet. D'you think this
school will ever really be ready?

rows.label: qst104208_msg0141

I think that should be enough, from
what Mason said. Thanks!

rows.label: qst104208_msg0161
rows.name:
Now I've got all the materials,
this is actually pretty exciting.
I hope this school turns out well!

rows.label: qst104208_msg0201
rows.name:
Apparently we've gotta crush all the
ores, then reform them together.

rows.label: qst104208_msg0202
rows.name: Mason's such a pro at this stuff!
